      <title>美国因投票问题制裁委内瑞拉法院院长和选举官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-sanctions-venezuela-court-chief-election-officials-over-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国周四宣布对委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的 16 名官员实施制裁，理由是他们涉嫌阻碍该国“自由公正”选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-sanctions-venezuela-court-chief-election-officials-over-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 14:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯支持汗对大型科技公司并购的做法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/vance-backs-khan-s-approach-on-big-tech-mergers-acquisitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党副总统候选人、俄亥俄州参议员 JD Vance 表示，一些大型科技合并可能会导致审查，这表明特朗普第二届政府可能会在反垄断监管方面采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/vance-backs-khan-s-approach-on-big-tech-mergers-acquisitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 14:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院在新任期内热衷于遏制机构权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/supreme-court-asked-to-curb-regulations-more-after-ending-chevron-deference-m0ze6lj2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国最高法院作出重磅裁决，削弱联邦机构监管企业的权力后，大政府的反对者们正在推行更加大胆的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/supreme-court-asked-to-curb-regulations-more-after-ending-chevron-deference-m0ze6lj2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 14:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国机构加大对刚果 15 岁以下儿童的 Mpox 应对力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/un-agency-scales-up-mpox-response-for-children-under-15-in-congo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国正在加强努力，遏制刚果民主共和国 15 岁以下儿童中疟疾的蔓延，该群体占疟疾死亡人数的大多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/un-agency-scales-up-mpox-response-for-children-under-15-in-congo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 14:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管裁决不成立，波兰仍将继续对央行行长进行调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/polish-lawmakers-to-press-on-with-probe-of-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰将继续对央行行长亚当格拉宾斯基 (Adam Glapinski) 进行调查，尽管有争议的法庭裁决称此类调查是非法的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/polish-lawmakers-to-press-on-with-probe-of-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅称俄罗斯导弹击中中立水域的粮食运输船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/russia-missile-hits-grain-ship-in-neutral-waters-zelenskiy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统泽连斯基在 Telegram 上表示，俄罗斯周四在一艘谷物船离开乌克兰水域后立即用导弹击中了该船。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/russia-missile-hits-grain-ship-in-neutral-waters-zelenskiy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:07:16 GMT</pubDate>
